<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[تخافتوا]</span>: أي تَسَارُّوا بالقول الخفي.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">قال الله تعالى:</span> فَانْطَلَقُوا وَهُمْ يَتَخاافَتُونَ <span class="c2">«٢»</span> قال: <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
